msgid "HELP_SIM_COMPOUND_DESC"
msgstr ""
"We calculate growth for each asset class individually. A 5% growth on a 100k "
"asset is calculated monthly to account for the compound effect over 30+ "
"years."

#: templates/core/help.html:177
msgid "HELP_SIM_DYNAMICS_DESC"
msgstr ""
"If you set a 2% \"Dynamics\" rate, your income doesn't stay level. It grows "
"every year, simulating career growth or contract-based indexing."

#: templates/core/help.html:183
msgid "HELP_SIM_30YEARS_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Retirement planning is a marathon. We chose a 30-year horizon to visualize "
"the late-stage effects of inflation and interest."

#: templates/core/help.html:203
msgid "HELP_DESIGN_HARMONY_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A \"Harmony\" isn't just a set of colors. It's a mathematical relationship "
"based on your Primary Color choice."

#: templates/core/help.html:205
msgid "HELP_DESIGN_GLASS_DESC"
msgstr ""
"We use backdrop filters and translucency to create depth. This allows your "
"personalized brand color to shine through."

#: templates/core/help.html:208
msgid "HELP_DESIGN_PROTIP_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Use a Darker background and high-vibrancy primary colors for the absolute "
"premium \"High-End\" look."

